Package com.distrimind.bouncycastle.jce

Class X509KeyUsage

java.lang.Object
com.distrimind.bouncycastle.asn1.ASN1Object
com.distrimind.bouncycastle.jce.X509KeyUsage
All Implemented Interfaces:
com.distrimind.bouncycastle.asn1.ASN1Encodable, com.distrimind.bouncycastle.util.Encodable
public class X509KeyUsage
extends com.distrimind.bouncycastle.asn1.ASN1Object
A holding class for constructing an X509 Key Usage extension. 
    id-ce-keyUsage OBJECT IDENTIFIER ::=  { id-ce 15 }

    KeyUsage ::= BIT STRING {
         digitalSignature        (0),
         nonRepudiation          (1),
         keyEncipherment         (2),
         dataEncipherment        (3),
         keyAgreement            (4),
         keyCertSign             (5),
         cRLSign                 (6),
         encipherOnly            (7),
         decipherOnly            (8) }
